Class WriteCSv

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Readable

    public class WriteCSv
extends java.lang.Object
implements Readable
    This class implements the Readable interface has two methods: First it reads WiggleWifi files and then it writes a new csv file. The new csv file has a different format and contains only certain data from the original WiggleWifi file.
